Description: everyone has a price
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Everyone has a price. What's yours? Take that concept and make a website out of it, and you get HowMutch, a price discovery engine. HowMutch asks its users various questions aimed at finding out how much it would take for you to do something unusual. For example, "How much would someone have to pay you to lick a subway pole?" After entering your personal price, HowMutch tells you how other people answered the same question, providing answer metrics (average, mean price, etc.) as well as the opportunity for you to share your answer with others on social media.  HowMutch also allows users to post their own questions, or watch as they vie with their friends to move up HowMutch's "Leaderboard."
Founders: Ari J. Greenberg, Gabriel Baldinucci, Jay Oh
